{% extends 'template/layout.njk' %}

{% block content %}

<h2>Get Started</h2>

<h3> Steps </h3>

<ol>

<li><code>npm install -g genysite</code></li>

<li>Create your site folder</li>

<li>Create the <code>src/pages/</code> folder, and set your nunjucks file inside it, subfolder, for arboresence</li>

<li>If you wanna use a template, set it inside the <code>src/template</code> folder</li>

<li>If you need some assets for your website, set it inside the <code>src/assets</code> folder</li>

<li>If your template need some assets, set it inside the <code>src/template/assets</code> folder</li>

<li>Run <code>genysite</code> inside your root folder</li>

</ol>

<h3>Template Filter</h3>

<ul>
  <li><b>link</b> <code>{% verbatim %}{{ "contact.html"|link }}{% endverbatim %}</code> will generate the path to the contact page <code>src/pages/contact.njk</code> </li>
<li><b>assets(isTemplateAssets = false)</b> <code><link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ 'milligram.css'|assets(true) }}"
</code></li>
</ul>

{% endblock %}
